name: 24 Suspended Moments
description:
24 notable hours in every day of the week 
Each moment sequential and totally unique
Singular memories of release and strength

For every hour of the day, a different video snippet of a different suspension is displayed. It changes every hour, on the hour. Time is specific to your locale. 

Interactive objkt forked from original code by Voltaine.
https://github.com/voltaine1/daynight
https://hen.link/Voltaine

All suspensions featured here were facilitated by me.
